307
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:13,010
I wouldn't say that...

308
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:16,020
Well, maybe it was.

309
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,520
Right?

310
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:20,020
But it wasn't like that for me at all.

311
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:23,710
I've been thinking this whole time...

312
00:15:23,710 --> 00:15:25,230
About how I want to go far away,

313
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:26,870
about how I hate being where I am,

314
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:28,280
about how I hate myself.

315
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:31,530
