350
00:17:42,410 --> 00:17:45,160
Don't worry. I'll keep myself safe.

351
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,740
See you later!

352
00:18:06,110 --> 00:18:07,730
Megu-chan?

353
00:18:07,730 --> 00:18:09,930
Sorry to bother you right before you set out.

354
00:18:09,930 --> 00:18:11,390
What's up?

355
00:18:11,390 --> 00:18:12,730
I came to break up.

356
00:18:14,990 --> 00:18:16,990
I'm saying, we're not friends anymore.

357
00:18:21,290 --> 00:18:23,390
What? What do you mean?

358
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:26,180
You still haven't realized it?

359
00:18:27,470 --> 00:18:32,300
