Antarctica going to Shinjuku came from?

360
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:34,000
Did you tell anyone about it?

361
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:36,210
No...

362
00:18:36,610 --> 00:18:38,980
The first time you met Antarctica,

363
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:42,420
how did those older girls 
know she had a million yen?

364
