to Antarctica before you told her?

365
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:48,600
How?

366
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:50,770
Because I told them, of course!

367
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:58,690
I thought you'd finally catch 
on and get mad at me...

368
00:18:58,690 --> 00:19:00,070
eventually...

369
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:00,990
Why?

370
00:19:00,990 --> 00:19:06,030
But you and Antarctica and the others 
are such morons you didn't catch on!

371
00:19:06,030 --> 00:19:06,950
Why?!

372
00:19:06,950 --> 00:19:07,960
I don't know!

373
00:19:10,370 --> 00:19:13,590
I don't know why I got so 
mad when you first told me

374
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:16,390
you were going to Antarctica!

375
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:22,230
You always consulted with me 
before you did anything...

376
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:24,720
No way... Wait a minute...

377
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:27,490
I know I've put you through a lot.

378
00:19:27,490 --> 00:19:28,230
I apologize.

379
00:19:28,580 --> 00:19:29,630
I'm sorry.

380
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:35,190
Yesterday, when you were 
talking, I finally realized.

381
00:19:35,610 --> 00:19:39,990
You weren't the one hanging on, I was.

382
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:44,920
